Map Legend 14

In this step lets see how to add a legend to map.

Steps for creating map legend

1.  Format data colors

  • Diverging  - on

                                      - Minimum - White 10% darker

                                     - Center - #f9bba9, theme color 8, 60% lighter

                                     - Maximum - #F15628

2. Then we take a screen shot of the rectangular box and save it.


3. Afterwards  you insert text box inside the map visualization, and write low and high, to help us identify the states with lowest and               highest infection

4. Then we insert the image of the diverging color inside the map.

5. At last , in the toolbar we go to format then click on Bring forward, select - Bring to front.
